#: ../../../appendix/supported-features.md:0
msgid "Heap Allocation (`Box`, `Vec`)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../appendix/supported-features.md:0
msgid ""
"CUDA has a device-side heap (`malloc`/`free` in kernels), and the compiler "
"allows the `alloc` crate through -- but no device-side `#[global_allocator]` "
"is wired up today. Even if it were, device `malloc` is extremely slow "
"(serialized, fragmented, uncoalesced). Use slices and `SharedArray`."
msgstr ""

